headline: Is It Too Late To Consider Cboe Global Markets (CBOE) After Its Strong Multi‑Year Run?
summary: If you are wondering whether Cboe Global Markets is still fairly priced after a strong run, this breakdown will help you make sense of what you are really paying for the stock. The share price recently closed at US$273.36, with returns of 3.1% over 7 days, 7.1% over 30 days, 10.2% year to date, 31.0% over 1 year, 125.0% over 3 years, and 228.0% over 5 years.
